@AdminRefreshToken = 7fvcSZT6x_2noGmZukWU3qLh5RoLVZrXwohNsmxkd1s
@UserToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..Z4NRUKvEM4PfvP0vXVtVWGMRctAYb-LcXXfK1qmvIls


### Login as admin
POST {{BaseAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}


### Admin endpoint (paste token to use)
GET {{BaseAddress}}/api/values/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{AdminToken}}


### User endpoint should fail for admin? (it will fail unless you treat Admin as User too)
GET {{BaseAddress}}/api/values/user
Authorization: Bearer {{AdminToken}}


### WhoAmI
GET {{BaseAddress}}/api/auth/whoami
Authorization: Bearer {{AdminToken}}


### Refresh (paste refresh token to use)
POST {{BaseAddress}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{AdminRefreshToken}}"
}


### Login as user
POST {{BaseAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user",
  "password": "user123"
}


### User endpoint (paste token)
GET {{BaseAddress}}/api/values/user
Authorization: Bearer {{UserToken}}


### Admin endpoint should fail for user
GET {{BaseAddress}}/api/values/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{UserToken}}